## Command Naming Convention

**Format**: `gbx:<category>:<action>`

| Category | Purpose | Commands |
|----------|---------|----------|
| `test` | Run tests | `scala`, `python`, `scala-docs`, `python-docs`, `sql-docs`, `docs`, `function-info` |
| `coverage` | Code coverage | `scala`, `scala-docs`, `python`, `python-docs` |
| `data` | Sample data | `download` |
| `docs` | Documentation | `start`, `stop`, `restart`, `function-info`, `prompt-session` |
| `docker` | Container mgmt | `exec`, `start`, `stop`, `restart`, `rebuild`, `attach` |

