- Custom port: `http://localhost:<port>`

### Log Files
- Server logs: `/tmp/docusaurus-<port>.log`
- PID file: `/tmp/docusaurus-<port>.pid`

### Build Output
- Location: `docs/build/`
- Generated by: `npm run build`
- Served by: `npm run serve`

